reap branch; F002 and F003 are supporting hardening/test gaps on the same release/reap surface.\",\"ruledOut\":[\"Hook relative-command rewrite targets were present and used runtime project-dir fallbacks in the three reviewed configs.\",\"SPEC_KIT_DB_DIR in the live durability test was not treated as a finding in this pass because the fake-root database directory also matches the launcher's derived database path.\"],\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.5-fast\"},\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-1-1780906361310-a9e1uj\",\"parentSessionId\":\"deep-review-139-multimodel\",\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-08T08:16:11Z\",\"durationMs\":0}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"synthesis_complete\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-1-1780906361310-a9e1uj\",\"parentSessionId\":\"deep-review-139-multimodel\",\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"totalIterations\":1,\"verdict\":\"CONDITIONAL\",\"activeP0\":0,\"activeP1\":1,\"activeP2\":2,\"dimensionCoverage\":1,\"hasAdvisories\":true,\"releaseReadinessState\":\"in-progress\",\"stopReason\":\"maxIterationsReached\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-08T08:16:11Z\"}\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-1/deep-review-findings-registry.json\n+{\n+  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55-1-1780906361310-a9e1uj\",\n+  \"generation\": 1,\n+  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n+  \"openFindings\": [\n+    {\n+      \"findingId\": \"F001\",\n+      \"severity\": \"P1\",\n+      \"category\": \"correctness\",\n+      \"dimension\": \"correctness\",\n+      \"finding_class\": \"class-of-bug\",\n+      \"title\": \"Stale-owner reclaim is not the spawn mutex the reap fix relies on\",\n+      \"file\": \".opencode/bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs\",\n+      \"line\": 468,\n+      \"lineRange\": \"468-481\",\n+      \"status\": \"active\",\n+      \"firstSeen\": 1,\n+      \"lastSeen\": 1,\n+      \"content_hash\": \"6d719d51c682e2144